  [LAMBDA (PHASE FONTSPECS FROMDIR DEVICE)                   (* ; "Edited  9-Jul-2026 16:49 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited  4-May-2026 08:59 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited  4-Apr-2026 11:41 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited  3-Apr-2026 00:51 by rmk")
