(FAKEFACE.FROMFONT
  [LAMBDA (FONTSPEC FROMDIR)                                 (* ; "Edited  3-May-2026 22:37 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited 19-Mar-2026 20:42 by rmk")

